                      <p>A passion for quality meats, superior customer service and providing customers with true family-friendly dining, Full Moon BBQ focuses on the overall experience.  At every location a hickory wood-fired pit provides full on flavor for every bite as their famous BBQ is cooked low and slow.  Full Moon BBQ is more than your next meal; it is a partner in creating community and making memories with Southern flare.</p>                  </article>
